The paper deals with object recognition in images, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method uses reinforcement learning, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The method involves adjusting parameters of operators, which can be related to robotics (cs.RO) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
